default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThe Government Agency which could ’prevent harm’default  the 
defaultTraffic Commissionersdefault act as the regulators of both drivers and operators of the vehicles which you are investi
defaultgating with regard to cyclist and pedestrian deaths and serious injuries.  The Commissioners have powers to revoke the vocational licences of drivers who fail the test of having good repute, and even enforcing a complete ban on driving. 
