defaultThe Commissioners can also call in operators who fail the conditions of good repute as well as 
defaultthe set criteria for management of their operations, if they get appropriate recognition and support in this work, but tellingly it is the restricted licence operators who are reported to be a prevailing feature of disciplinary hearings. These operators, c
defaultarrying only their own goods, are exempt from the requirement to have a qualified transport manager, and various other provisions placed on domestic and international operators. Many waste management operators are operating with restricted licences, a deta
defaultil highlighted by Jack Semple of RHA in his evidence to the Committee. 
